00:30:41.067 --> 00:30:46.114
Her arm got caught in a forklift, trapped between a big bag of rice.

00:30:54.030 --> 00:30:54.220
It almost ripped her arm out of the socket and completely off her body.

00:30:54.220 --> 00:31:04.320
After seven surgeries, she could not lift her hand above her head, but by the power of God, she was raising her hand in church.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
It was amazing to see an arm that was almost completely ripped off.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God is so good; it is just the beginning.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We stand by Jesus the healer, the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We hope it blessed you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
This is stuff that we needed to say and pray.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
That prayer for Kari Lake was definitely necessary.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus loves you, and we love you.
